               <p>Brown's Defence.</p>
               <p>I know nothing of the handkerchief, nor of this Litners.</p>
               <p>Litner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I never touched the lad's pocket; I never saw Brown before. I carried meat out for the butchers in Brooks-market.</p>
